  <summary date="2020-06-30T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Don't Block LGBTQ Act of 2020

This bill prohibits elementary schools, secondary schools, or libraries that receive discount rates for telecommunications services&#160;under the universal service support program from blocking internet access to lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, or queer resources.

The bill does not prohibit schools or libraries from blocking content that is obscene, child pornography, or harmful to minors.</summary>
